summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of the south 6 ft. of Lot 18 and all of Lots 19 and 20, Block 55, Boston Company's Plat of West Seattle, with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-456 and 17-329, respectively.
